# Release Notes — ENDOS V1.5

## Sprint 5: Dynamic Knowledge Graph

This release introduces the first connected object view for ENDOS. It is intentionally lightweight and static, but it establishes the structural foundation for a future repository-driven enterprise knowledge graph.

## Included

- Knowledge Graph page
- Graph JavaScript renderer
- Static graph object data
- Knowledge Graph documentation
- Updated changelog and README

## Next Sprint Candidate

Sprint 6: Validation Center — replay cases and evidence logic.
